@startuml system_architecture
!define RECTANGLE class

title 智能视频分析系统 - 系统整体架构图

package "数据采集层" {
    [视频设备\n摄像头/RTSP] as VideoDevice
    [VideoSource\n视频采集模块] as VideoSource
}

package "数据处理层" {
    queue "VideoFrameQueue<cv::Mat>\n采集队列" as CaptureQueue
    [YOLOv11Detector\n目标检测推理引擎] as Detector
    queue "VideoFrameQueue<FrameData>\n检测队列" as DetectQueue
}

package "数据输出层" {
    [FFmpegPush\nRTSP推流模块] as FFmpegPush
    [VideoRecorder\n视频录制模块] as Recorder
    [MediaMTX\nRTSP服务器] as MediaMTX
    database "本地存储\nrecordings/" as Storage
}

package "Web管理层" {
    [Flask Web Server\napp.py] as Flask
    [前端界面] as Frontend
    [API接口] as API
    [流管理] as StreamMgr
    [设备管理] as DeviceMgr
    [模型管理] as ModelMgr
    [系统监控] as SysMonitor
}

VideoDevice --> VideoSource
VideoSource --> CaptureQueue
CaptureQueue --> Detector
Detector --> DetectQueue
DetectQueue --> FFmpegPush
DetectQueue --> Recorder
FFmpegPush --> MediaMTX
Recorder --> Storage
MediaMTX --> Frontend : HLS流

Flask --> Frontend
Flask --> API
API --> StreamMgr
API --> DeviceMgr
API --> ModelMgr
API --> SysMonitor

@enduml

@startuml inference_dataflow
title 核心推理模块数据流图

|输入预处理|
start
:原始帧 cv::Mat;
:图像缩放 Letterbox;
:填充Padding 640x640;
:归一化 1/255.0;
:通道转换 BGR→RGB;
:张量构建 1x3x640x640;

|模型推理|
if (推理后端选择?) then (ONNX Runtime)
    :YOLOv11Detector ONNX;
elseif (LibTorch) then
    :YOLOv11Detector Torch;
else (TensorRT)
    :YOLOv11RT TRT;
endif
:GPU/CPU推理;

|后处理|
:输出解析 8400个锚点;
:置信度过滤 conf_thresh;
:类别过滤 target_classes;
:NMS非极大值抑制 nms_thresh;
:坐标映射 还原到原图;
:检测结果 Detection;

stop
@enduml

@startuml thread_dataflow
title 多线程数据流图

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "ThreadPool 线程池" {
    [Thread 1\n视频采集线程] as T1
    [Thread 2\n推理检测线程] as T2
    [Thread 3\n帧处理线程] as T3
    [Thread 4\n录制监控线程] as T4
}

package "共享队列" {
    queue "capture_queue\nVideoFrameQueue<cv::Mat>" as Q1
    queue "detect_queue\nVideoFrameQueue<FrameData>" as Q2
}

[VideoSource] as VS
[FFmpegPush] as FP
[VideoRecorder] as VR

VS -down-> Q1 : Push
Q1 -down-> T2 : Pop
T2 -down-> Q2 : Push
Q2 -down-> T3 : Pop
T3 -down-> FP : Push
T3 -down-> VR : Notify

T1 ..> VS : 控制
T4 ..> VR : 监控

@enduml

@startuml detector_class
title 推理引擎类图

class YOLOv11Detector_ONNX {
    - Ort::Env env
    - Ort::Session* session
    - Ort::MemoryInfo* memory_info
    - int input_size
    - float conf_thresh
    - float nms_thresh
    - vector<string> class_names
    - set<int> target_class_ids
    - VideoFrameQueue* input_queue
    - VideoFrameQueue* output_queue
    + Init() bool
    + detect(cv::Mat) vector<Detection>
    + draw_detections() cv::Mat
    + start() void
    - preprocess() vector<float>
    - postprocess() vector<Detection>
}

class YOLOv11Detector_Torch {
    - torch::jit::script::Module model
    - torch::Device device
    - vector<string> class_names
    - int input_size
    - float conf_thresh
    - float nms_thresh
    + YOLOv11Detector()
    + detect(cv::Mat) vector<Detection>
}

class YOLOv11RT {
    - nvinfer1::ICudaEngine* engine
    - nvinfer1::IExecutionContext* context
    - void* device_input_buffer
    - void* device_output_buffer
    - Logger logger
    + init() bool
    - buildEngine() bool
    - loadEngine() bool
    - preprocess() void
    - postprocess() vector<Detection>
}

class Detection {
    + cv::Rect bbox
    + float confidence
    + int class_id
    + string class_name
}

class FrameData {
    + cv::Mat frame
    + vector<Detection> detections
    + int64_t timestamp_ms
    + int64_t frame_id
    + bool has_person
}

YOLOv11Detector_ONNX --> Detection : 生成
YOLOv11Detector_Torch --> Detection : 生成
YOLOv11RT --> Detection : 生成
FrameData *-- Detection : 包含

@enduml

@startuml web_api_sequence
title Web API数据流时序图

actor 前端
participant Flask
participant StreamManager
participant VideoPush
participant MediaMTX

前端 -> Flask : POST /api/streams (创建流配置)
Flask -> StreamManager : save_stream()
StreamManager --> Flask : 配置已保存
Flask --> 前端 : 成功响应

前端 -> Flask : POST /api/streams/{id}/start
Flask -> StreamManager : start_stream_process()
StreamManager -> VideoPush : 启动VideoPush.exe
VideoPush -> MediaMTX : RTSP推流
MediaMTX --> 前端 : HLS流可用

前端 -> Flask : GET /api/streams/{id}/status
Flask -> StreamManager : get_stream_status()
StreamManager --> Flask : 运行状态
Flask --> 前端 : 状态信息

前端 -> Flask : POST /api/streams/{id}/stop
Flask -> StreamManager : stop_stream_process()
StreamManager -> VideoPush : 终止进程
VideoPush --> Flask : 进程已终止
Flask --> 前端 : 成功响应

@enduml

